-- out/todo.txt --
patternCycle.t1.{p1,p2,p3}: v2 had cyclic pattern constraint errors; v3 resolves correctly.
issue3638.full.entrypoint and issue3638.full.#Kubernetes.input.res1: v3 uses structure sharing (~), v2 expands.
issue3638.reduced.out.foo: v3 has only one disjunct ({a:1}); v2 has two (*(a:1,b:2) | {a:1}).
d field ordering: v3 puts foobar before foo; v2 puts foo before foobar.
